Usage: deleteModulePort [-help] <moduleName> <portName> [-bus <startId:endId>]

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
<moduleName>             # Name of module or use '-' as root (string, required)
<portName>               # Name of the port (string, required)
-bus <startId:endId>     # bus bit startId:endId (string, optional)